# Known Issues & Solutions

## High Priority (P0) - Critical UX Issues

### 1. Generic Error Messages
**Files**: 
- [app/components/ErrorBoundary.tsx](mdc:app/components/ErrorBoundary.tsx)
- [app/components/ApprovalCard.tsx](mdc:app/components/ApprovalCard.tsx)

**Issues**:
- "Something went wrong" - too generic
- "Failed to approve/reject" - no context

**Solutions**: See [docs/design/error_message_localization_audit.md](mdc:docs/design/error_message_localization_audit.md)

### 2. HTTP Errors Exposed
**Files**:
- [app/routes/approvals.$id.$idx.approve/route.tsx](mdc:app/routes/approvals.$id.$idx.approve/route.tsx)
- [app/routes/approvals.$id.$idx.reject/route.tsx](mdc:app/routes/approvals.$id.$idx.reject/route.tsx)
- [app/utils/api-client.server.ts](mdc:app/utils/api-client.server.ts)

**Issue**: Raw HTTP status codes shown to users

**Solution**: Transform to user-friendly via error handler utility

### 3. Missing Help Text
**Files**:
- [app/components/ApprovalCard.tsx](mdc:app/components/ApprovalCard.tsx)
- Dashboard tile components

**Issue**: No tooltips or help for key actions

**Solution**: Add helpText props and tooltips. See [docs/design/help_text_localization_audit.md](mdc:docs/design/help_text_localization_audit.md)

## Medium Priority (P1) - Infrastructure

### 4. No Centralized Copy Repository
**Issue**: Copy hardcoded in components

**Solution**: Create `app/copy/` directory with centralized files (see rule 13-copy-centralization.mdc)

### 5. No Translation Key System
**Issue**: No i18n infrastructure

**Solution**: Implement translation keys with centralized copy

### 6. Missing Transactional Emails
**Issue**: Password reset, order confirmation templates not located

**Solution**: Audit and create transactional email templates

## Low Priority (P2) - Features

### 7. No Hot Rod AN Theme Toggle
**Issue**: Only professional voice available

**Solution**: Implement theme toggle per [docs/design/hot_rod_an_voice_tone_guide.md](mdc:docs/design/hot_rod_an_voice_tone_guide.md)

